// ChatDrawer
// Left-side slide-in drawer containing the full message list and auto-scroll behavior.
// Renders AI UI components inline with chat messages.

FUNCTION handleAction(actionId, payload)
  Dispatches an action response to chatStore.

---

FUNCTION ChatDrawer(props) -> ReactNode                                   EXPORT
  CALLS: useChatStore (chatStore), AIUIRenderer (renderer)
  Reads messages and open state from chatStore.
  IF closed, renders nothing (or a collapsed rail).
  IF open, renders a full-height side drawer with the message list and auto-scroll to the latest message.
  Renders each message with AIUIRenderer for AI UI component blocks.
  Passes handleAction to AIUIRenderer for interactive components.
